headline: DaVita Statement on Government's Kidney Care Choices (KCC) Model Updates
summary: DaVita, a comprehensive kidney care company, issued the following statement in response to updates this week from the Center for Medicare and Medicaid Innovation (CMMI) related to its Kidney Care Choices (KCC) Model. It can be attributed to Misha Palecek, chief transformation officer for DaVita.
